19.title: Whizzy William
19.plot: William, the straight-faced Soviet Union spy under the code-name Maxwell decides to go to the amusement park. Grandpa, CIA agent, goes with his grandchildren in an attempt to foil his plans, and hides in their pockets. However, Grandpa fails to foil his plans before William foils his own plan. William goes on the carousel, making himself whizzy, and bringing himself right into Grandpa's welcoming arms.
